Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki is guilty of\Nfirst-degree offenses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:41.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and will be executed in 25 days\Nat the Central Execution Grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:46.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the final decision\Nof the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were very calm,\NCaptain of Squad 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:04.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such calmness in the wake\Nof your sister's execution…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:08.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed a role model\Nfor Soul Reapers, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:13.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You and the Captain of Squad 9 are\Nthe only Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who would fret over dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:23.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now what would two Captains\Nwithout their aides want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:29.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we were just...\Nconcerned that the Captain of Squad 6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:33.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would be feeling low because\Nhis sister was about to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our family lineage is\Nnone of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not upset, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals are such\Na bother to the nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my… how unusual for a commoner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to understand\Nthe subtleties of nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:51.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. I've always been\Nthe sensitive one since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:52.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just to show my sensitivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:59.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’d even offer to chop off the\Ncriminal's head, before the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:04.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware that at your present level\Nyou could fell a person's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Forgive us, Captain of Squad 6.\N– Hey! Ichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– I never intended to offend you in any way.\N– Let go! Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going now.\NMy regards to your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You're all right, Tessai!\NI mean, Mr. Tessai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses are in terrible shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you're okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, keep those glasses\Non even if they're cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:56.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The owner drew his sword,\Nand it's getting very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can't miss this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, even with that\Nwisp of a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean\NI'll go easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a minute!\NHold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Zanpaku-to was\Nthe only sword
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that could kill Soul Reapers\Nand Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:23.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He pulled that sword from his cane.\NIt can't be a Zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then even if he did get me,\Nit wouldn't hurt me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You let down your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:34.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"He's not a Soul Reaper,\Nso it can't be a Zanpaku-to."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"So I can't get hurt even\Nif he cuts me." Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:40.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are so naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Benihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:51.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Zanpaku-to,\Ntotally authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Benihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even ask the name\Nof your Zanpaku-to! A guy like you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpaku-to’s…name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Each Zanpaku-to has a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:17.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And this is...her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:18.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Benihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I compliment you for not running away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:30.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and countering my sword\Nwith that broken one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's some courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:39.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Benihime isn't so kind that\Nshe'd let a sword like that stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way can that be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He cut my Zanpaku-to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you told?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:55.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your sword is big.\NBut that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no concentration of\Nspiritual energy in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:02.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It just distends and holds its shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,cut it easily like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now you don't have a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still attack me with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you just have\Nto knock my hat off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it with that hilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:28.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, it won't be just\Ncourage or guts that's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just warn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you still intend to fight me\Nwith that toy…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die! I'll really be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I running?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the extent of\Nmy determination?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disgusted with myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:02.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– helpless!\N– You are so…helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:10.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you run, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't called me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look ahead, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to hear it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:30.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is fear that makes\Nyou shut your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one enemy,\Nand only one you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?\NBoth of them stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon your fears!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you retreat,\Nyou'll only grow old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you fear, you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Call it out! My name is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:21.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that Zanpaku-to…?\NThere's no hilt or hand guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even shaped\Nlike a proper sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The other one was better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well now…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have your Zanpaku-to,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,shall we start\NLesson Three in earnest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mr. Urahara…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:14.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have it mastered yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Benihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Without this Shield of Blood Mist…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have lost an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:49.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My hat's torn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd do it in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,one swing…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are one frightening kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson Three cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. It’s complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:31.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Terrific, Chad! You did it! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Know your limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the panic you've caused!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now run away from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:42.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But how unexpected…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that they could awaken\Ntheir powers in such a short time…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad has fallen down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.07,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aug 1, 6:30pm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.08,DefaultLow,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After completing my training\Nat Urahara Shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to stay at home while
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:11.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they prepare to open the gate\Nto the Soul Society, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:16.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And here we are at\Nthe long-awaited Fireworks Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! How can you not be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely, young 'un!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:26.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, I have special seats\Nthat I've saved since seven this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding! Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Terrific!\NSometimes you're useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And how about you\Ncute ladies over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:35.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be there later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, oh well… I guess I'll join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Tatsuki, it's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to come\Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:53.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Don't worry.\NI'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is so energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say. It's tiring sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki, does your hand hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Although, if I think about how this\Ncaused me to lose first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it does hurt a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But second place in\Nthe Inter-High Tournament means
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're the second strongest\Nhigh school girl in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Tatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes…You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:30.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been such a long time\Nsince we last came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We only come in autumn each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:39.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My brother had this terrific knack\Nfor catching red dragonflies on his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'd point his fingers to the sky\Nand immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a dragonfly would land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was like magic and\NI loved to watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:50.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to be able\Nto do that…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're visiting relatives\Nfrom next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo said he's going on\Na trip next week, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be first…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:20.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never regretted trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:23.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't turn out well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:27.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there are things you discover\Njust by doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So…so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've decided,\Ngo forward and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And in exchange…I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:45.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting here…so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.53,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aug. 8, 1:00am
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:16.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In seven days, at 1:00am,\Nleave your window open and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting bad vibes all over…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nice breeze…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:38.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the front\Nof Urahara Shop immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like a dying message\Nat a murder scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it comes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this… P.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you thought this was\N "like a dying message"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or something common like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you have no sense of humor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:14.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yuzu, Karin…Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dodging that attack…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– you ARE my son, after all.\N– What the hell are you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:27.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,B-Before you leave,\NI want to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:30.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this amulet…so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:34.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call it dirty!\NYour mother gave it to me long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is filled with luck\Nand divine grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing?!\NI can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right!\NWho'd give it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to lend it\Nto you during your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After you return, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here! What do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:59.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You give it back, you hear?!\NI'll shave if you lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:04.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Slaying a Hollow does\Nnot mean killing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it a Hollow...\Nthat killed your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So many things have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you grab\Nmy brother like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will die anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so stay there and live\Neven one more second longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it be like\N it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad…why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:56.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki once saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way will I remain defeated\Nby those Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:23.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Hey! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty slow on the up-take,\Naren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, don't tell me you didn't notice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the increase in the hidden powers\Nof these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While you were training\Nto regain your Soul Reaper power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:42.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,these three were also training\Nin their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:46.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of criticizing,\Nbow your head and thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A cat just spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– He's not a cat. He's Yoruichi.\N– A-A cat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it is shocking, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s his first time meeting him, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes… that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:04.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't keep talking outside.\NLet's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean…it's going to\Nbe dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:22.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Tatsuki that\NI'd go with you. And…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:38.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow! All this space\Nbeneath the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is so neat…\Nit's like a secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:47.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful reaction!\NI, Tessai, am deeply moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, your attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the gate that leads\Nto Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's known as Senkaimon,\Nwhich is written, "Tunnel World Gate."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:07.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen very carefully. Before that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– It's so easy to come out.\N– Hey, warn me, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Ichigo is no longer inside Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!\NDon't talk like I'm not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This gate has\Na layer of Reishihenkanki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:24.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit-particle Conversion Machine\Non top of a normal Senkaimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit-particle… Conversion Machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:31.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know,\Nthe Soul Society is a world of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is impossible to enter that\Nworld unless you have the form of a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:40.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, only Ichigo,\Nas a Soul Reaper, can cross through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:44.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So we will use the Henkanki\Nto convert you into spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:49.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even without extracting our spirits,\Nby going through this gate…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:54.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will be able to enter\Nthe Soul Society like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Let's...!\N– However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The time that we have\Nto open the gate and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:04.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,connect it to the Soul Society is…\Nfour minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that enough time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reckless idea to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my very best and\Nhold it for four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't cross over in that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:24.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will be trapped forever between\Nthe Soul Society and this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that the heart\Nand soul are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is\Nwhat you feel in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the will to move it forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:40.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will be your guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:45.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who can\Ndo that can follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you babbling in\Nyour sleep or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, kid,\Nthat if you fail, you cannot return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I just have to win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run in the instant it opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:31.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:52.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:54.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:10.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:12.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:26.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:30.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:32.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:37.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:39.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– It's a mountain.\N– It's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:41.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a gatekeeper giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:44.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you have it.\NKurosaki, you handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:45.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Go for it!\N– You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:46.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:49.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Huh?\NErr...I guess I am!